title.rendered: ZKTECO INBIO 460 CASE B IP-BASED DOOR ACCESS CONTROL PANEL

content.rendered:
inBio 460 is a four Door Access Control Panel

Features

  • User – 30,000
  • Event Buffer – 100,000 transactions
  • Communication – TCP/IP
  • Number of doors controlled – 4 door
  • Number of readers Supported – (8 RS-485 Reader, 4 26-bit wiegand reader)
  • Types of readers supported – 26-bit Wiegand and RS485 FR Series Reader
  • Number of Inputs – 12( 4 Exit Button, 4 Door Status, 4 AUX)
  • Number of Outputs – 8 (4-Form C Relay or Lock and 4-Form C Relay for Aux Output).
